        "## How to use AllenNLP's Named Entity Recognition (NER)\n",
        "\n",
        "AllenNLP Demo: https://demo.allennlp.org/named-entity-recognition/named-entity-recognition\n",
        "\n",
        "B stands for Beginning of a named entity\n",
        "I stands for Inside of a named entity\n",
        "\n",
        "The text will be annotated in 9 classes:\n",
        "*   B-PER / I-PER = Person\n",
        "*   B-LOC / I-LOC = Location \n",
        "*   B-ORG / I-ORG = Organization \n",
        "*   B-MISC / I-MISC = Miscellaneous \n",
        "*   0 = No named entity\n",
        "\n"

        "## How to use Spacy's NER\n",
        "\n",
        "English Spacy NER has ca. 19 categories:\n",
        "*   CARDINAL – other numerals\n",
        "*   DATE\n",
        "*   EVENT – named hurricanes, wars, sport events\n",
        "*   FAC – Buildings, airports, highways, bridges\n",
        "*   GPE – coutries, cities, states\n",
        "*   LANGUAGE\n",
        "*   LAW – named documents made into laws\n",
        "*   LOC – Locations\n",
        "*   Non-GPE - mountain ranges, bodies of water\n",
        "*   MONEY\n",
        "*   NORP - nationalities, religious or political groups\n",
        "*   ORDINAL – first, second, third\n",
        "*   ORG – companies, agencies, institutions\n",
        "*   PERCENT\n",
        "*   PERSON\n",
        "*   PRODUCT\n",
        "*   QUANTITY – weight, measure\n",
        "*   TIME – times smaller than a day\n",
        "*   WORK_OF_ART – paintings, books, songs\n"
